data.description: Stunning remodeled 3/2.5/2 home in the desirable Country Club Estates! Great home with 2 living areas and 2 dining areas.  Beautiful kitchen with quartz counter tops, stainless steel appliances and plenty of cabinet space.  Beautiful flooring and paint colors throughout the home.  Living room has a wet bar and gorgeous brick fireplace. 2nd living room is perfect for a pool table/game room or a large office. Spacious primary suite with  private access to backyard.  Master bath has dual vanities & tiled walk in shower!. Generous size laundry room with built in desk and half bath.  Pool size backyard and outdoor patio for entertaining. 2020 Roof and 2023 A/C.  Golf course right around the corner from this home. Close to fine restaurants, shopping and great schools.  Minutes away from: Beach, Oso Wetland Preserve, CC Naval Base, and A&M Island University.  Be sure to view the virtual TOUR link! This home will go fast!
